@startuml
title Permissions Access Matrix

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam backgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam classBackgroundColor #E0F2FE
skinparam classBorderColor #0EA5E9
skinparam classFontColor #0F172A
skinparam classHeaderBackgroundColor #BAE6FD
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEF3C7
skinparam noteBorderColor #F59E0B
skinparam noteFontColor #78350F

class "Access Matrix" as AccessMatrix {
  |= Role |= Payroll |= Financial Reports |= Employee Records |= Audit Logs |
  | Employee | No Access | No Access | Own Only | No Access |
  | HR | Read / Update | No Access | Manage | No Access |
  | Finance Analyst | No Access | Read | No Access | No Access |
  | Manager | No Access | Read-Only | Limited | No Access |
  | Admin | Full Access | Full Access | Full Access | Full Access |
}

note bottom of AccessMatrix
Least privilege is enforced by granting each role
only the permissions required for its responsibilities.
Separation of duties is supported by dividing access
between HR, Finance, Management, and Administration.
end note

@enduml